When you are on the road our app is your friend! Enjoy a range of different digital services that are constantly evolving to give you the best possible Circle K experience.

Google Gemini app is your personal, proactive and powerful AI assistant.

With Gemini on your iPhone or iPad, you can:

– Go Live with Gemini to brainstorm ideas, simplify complex topics and rehearse for important moments. Share your camera or screen in Gemini Live conversations to talk with Gemini about anything that you see. Just click on the Gemini Live button in your Gemini app
– Bring your ideas to life with Canvas. From prompt to prototype, create apps, games, web pages, infographics, Audio Overviews and more
– Connect with your favourite Google apps, like Search, YouTube, Google Maps, Gmail and more
– Study smarter and explore any topic with quiz and flashcard creation, interactive visuals and real-world examples
– Turn any file into a podcast that you can listen to any time, anywhere
– Create and edit stunning images from just a few words
– Plan trips better and faster
– Get summaries, deep dives and source links, all in one place
– Brainstorm new ideas or improve existing ones

Try Nano Banana: State-of-the-art image generation and editing built on Gemini 2.5 Flash


Level up your Gemini app experience by upgrading to the Plus plan – unlock new and powerful features to boost your creativity and productivity:
– Get more access to our most powerful models, like 2.5 Pro
– Generate and dive into detailed reports on any topic with Deep Research powered by 2.5 Pro
– Turn words into high-quality, eight-second video clips with video generation with Veo 3.1 Fast and more.

Google AI Plus includes additional benefits. Gemini app, as part of Google AI Plus, will be available to qualifying Google Workspace business and education plans. Learn more: https://gemini.google/subscriptions/

Get even more out of your Gemini app experience by upgrading to the Pro plan, which helps you tackle complex tasks and projects. Enjoy an industry-leading 1M token context window (enabling Gemini to process up to 1,500 pages of text or 30k lines of code), and higher access to our most capable model 2.5 Pro, Deep Research on 2.5 Pro and video generation with Veo 3.1 Fast.

Gemini in Google AI Pro includes additional benefits as part of a Google AI Pro subscription. The Gemini app, as part of Google AI Pro, will continue to be available to qualifying Google Workspace business and education plans. Learn more: https://gemini.google/subscriptions/

Get the best of Gemini app by upgrading to the Ultra plan – unlock the highest level of access to the best of Google AI and exclusive features. Get the highest access to Google's most powerful model, like 2.5 Pro, features like video generation with Veo 3.1, Deep Research on 2.5 Pro and unlock Gemini 2.5 Deep Think. You'll also get early access to try our newest AI innovations as they become available, including Agent Mode.

Gemini in Google AI Ultra includes additional benefits as part of a Google AI Ultra subscription. Google AI Ultra for Business is available as an add-on to Google Workspace customers. Learn more: https://support.google.com/a/answer/16345165

The Google Gemini mobile app is available in selected languages and countries. Learn more:
g.co/gemini/iosrequirements

Gemini Live feature availability varies based on language. Learn more:
g.co/gemini/ioslanguages

While Gemini can help you with many tasks like checking the weather, giving directions, and finding and summarising information across the web and apps, Gemini does not yet support device actions like setting an alarm, sending a text message and others on iOS.

Review the Gemini Apps Privacy Notice:
g.co/gemini/privacynotice

description:
Programėlė skirta padėti Lietuvos gyventojams pasiruošti netikėtoms situacijoms bei greitai reaguoti ekstremaliųjų įvykių metu. 
Funkcijos ir galimybės:
•        Realiuoju laiku  gaunami svarbūs perspėjimo pranešimai apie ekstremaliąsias situacijas, pvz., gamtines nelaimes, avarijas ar kitas grėsmes. 
•        Galimybė žemėlapyje rasti artimiausią priedangą (oro pavojaus atveju), kolektyvinės apsaugos statinį (saugiam apsistojimui), gyventojų surinkimo punktą (evakuacijos atveju) bei sužinoti, kur arčiausiai nelaimės atveju gaustų perspėjimo sirena.
•        Veiksmų seka/algoritmas, kaip elgtis oro pavojaus (pvz., iškilus karo grėsmei)  ar galimos radiologinės/branduolinės avarijos atveju, taip pat kitoms galimoms gamtinėms ar stichinėms nelaimėms.
•        Civilinės saugos žinių patikrinimo testas.
•        Būtiniausių daiktų ir priemonių sąrašas bei informacija, kaip susidėti išvykimo krepšį.
•        Pasiruošimui skirta edukacinė vaizdo informacija 
•        Naudingos nuorodos ir patarimai, kaip nelaimės atveju apsaugoti save ir artimuosius
•        
•        Kodėl verta naudotis?
Būk pasiruošęs bet kokiai situacijai ir užtikrink savo bei artimųjų saugumą. Programėlė LT72 yra oficialus įrankis, kuris padės apsaugoti gyvybę ir turtą, greitai reaguojant į nelaimes.
•        Nemokama ir lengvai naudojama.
•        Parsisiųsk dabar ir pasiruošk ateičiai!

myDPD app offers a wide range of functions.

The Zalando app is your new go-to for quality fashion and lifestyle brands (over 6,000!), outfit and beauty inspiration at your fingertips, and a shopping experience that’s all smooth and no stress.

IT'S GIVING INSPIRATION
• Follow your favourite creators for outfit and styling inspo
• Follow brands you like to see more from them first, including new releases and exclusive collections
• Curate and follow boards of the outfits, videos, and products that inspire you, and start inspiring others
• Explore what’s trending across Europe with Trend Spotter and see what everyone’s wearing in Berlin, Paris, and Milan right now
• Tune into our Live videos to get tips from the experts, product how-tos, and inspo you can add directly to your bag
• Tap into Stories to get your style and culture guide with features like “What do I wear?” plus the latest on major brand collabs
• Save your faves to your wishlist and never miss a size update or price drop

IT'S GIVING CHOICE
• Browse over 11,000 items from a wide range of brands, including all-time fashion favourites
• Dive into our different assortments: clothing, shoes, accessories, sports, beauty and skincare, preloved gems, and kidswear
• Get updates on the things you care about - from news and trends to sales and discount codes
• Hear about new collections and product launches from the brands you love
• Never miss a price drop or restock by opting in to notifications on items in your wishlist
• Give preloved clothing a new life when you shop our extensive selection of pre-owned (but just like new!) clothing, accessories, and boots
Pick your preferred way to pay and enjoy delivery directly to your own doorstep

IT'S GIVING PERSONAL
• Benefit from spot-on recommendations that show you the items you’ll love, without you needing to go looking for them
• Rate how the fashion you’ve ordered fits and get personalised sizing advice as you shop
• Get measured with our measurements tool to find what fits, fast
• Try on outfits in our virtual fitting room to see how they’ll fit before ordering
• Get instant style and outfit advice from the Zalando Assistant, a tailor-made AI-powered fashion assistant to help you on your shopping journey

So, ready to explore the app?
Shop the brands you love, unlock exclusive deals, and get inspiration and recommendations that feel like they were made just for you.

Shop brands you love:

- Shop big brands and local stores, and follow your faves
- Get notified about special offers, price drops, restocks, and new product drops
- Save items for later and organize things into collections (like “camping gear” or “ideas for dad”)
- Just so you know: brands don’t pay extra to sell on Shop, which means each time you buy, you’re helping out the business

Check out with one tap:

- Your payment info, shipping address, and shopping preferences all live in your secure Shop Pay wallet
- Just tap to check out (no more getting up to go find your card)
- Every shopping cart from every store is saved on Shop, so it’s all there when you’re ready to check out
- Just so you know: your info is safe with Shop, which meets strict PCI compliance standards

Track all your orders:

- See every order from every store you buy from
- Map exactly where each package is now
- Shop can even scan your email for new order info and collect it for you in the app (no more searching your inbox for updates) 

- - -

Have a question or just want to say hello? Contact us by visiting help.shop.app

Shop secure and worry free: Our servers meet strict PCI compliance standards for vaulting credit card info.

Powered by Shopify: Shop was created by the commerce platform trusted by millions of businesses worldwide.

Join the millions of riders who trust Uber for their everyday travel needs. Whether you’re running an errand across town or exploring a city far from home, getting there should be easy.

FIND THE RIDE YOU WANT
Find the perfect ride right at your fingertips! Uber is here to make your journey stress-free and enjoyable, whether you're requesting a taxi for a trip or arranging a train journey.

Pick from a wide range of travel options that the Uber app has to offer including:
UberX: Affordable, everyday rides
Lux: Luxury cars with top-rated drivers for premium travel experiences
Electric: Sustainable rides in electric vehicles for eco-friendly trips
UberXL: Rides for groups up to 6, perfect for family trips
Comfort: Newer cars with extra legroom to enhance your travel
Uber Pet: Ride with your pet
Reserve: Choose your exact pickup time up to 90 days in advance for planned trips
Exec: High-end cars with top-rated drivers, ideal for business travel
2-wheels: You can also bike or ride a scooter with the Uber app. Find a scooter to start riding today for quick trips
Assist: Special assistance from trained drivers for accessible travel
Access: Wheelchair accessible vehicles ensuring inclusivity in travel
Black Cab: travel with the iconic London taxi

UPFRONT PRICING
With Uber, you no longer need to worry about hidden costs or unexpected surprises. As you enter your destination in the app, you get upfront pricing and the estimated time of arrival, whether it's a taxi ride or train. 

SAFETY TOGETHER
Safety is a top priority at Uber. We have established comprehensive safety features to help ensure every rider and driver feels secure and comfortable in their travel and on trips.

AFFORDABLE PRICING
We’re doing all we can to make our pricing as transparent as possible.
Split Fare: Don’t worry about doing the math later—split the cost evenly while you’re still on the ride.

JOIN UBER ONE FOR EXCLUSIVE PERKS
Benefit from £0 Delivery Fee and up to 5% off eligible delivery and pickup orders, 5-10% off eligible rides, and £5 credit if our Latest Arrival Estimate on your order is off. Other fees & terms apply. For more details see uber.com/uberone.

RESERVE RIDES IN ADVANCE
Need a ride at a specific time? No problem! Uber allows you to reserve rides in advance, so you can plan your day with confidence. Extra wait time included to meet your ride. Cancel at no charge up to 60 minutes in advance.

TRAVEL
Get train, coach, and flight ticketing right on the Uber app. Get 10% back in Uber Credits and collect Avios when you book train, coach, and Eurostar trips. No booking fee. Make any flight flexible and refundable and avoid flight travel stress with flight disruption protection.

GO GREEN
Uber is committed to building a sustainable future for our cities. With a growing fleet of electric and hybrid vehicles, you can choose eco-friendly rides to reduce your carbon footprint.

RENT CARS
Whether you need a car today or later, the online booking experience will help you find the right vehicle for a family vacation, a weekend getaway, airport travel, and more. Get great prices & selection from the best rental companies.

MORE FEATURES
Delivery: Order food from your favourite restaurants through Uber Eats. Stock up on groceries, shop pharmacy, convenience, and pet supplies, and get them all delivered.
Uber Boat: Get fast, reliable river boat services in London. For commuters and visitors. Routes run from 24 piers across the capital.
Uber for Business: Manage and track business travel, meal programs, and more on one dashboard.

Uber is available in the following cities: London, Manchester, Leeds, Glasgow, and more. Check if Uber is available in your city at https://www.uber.com/cities. Stay updated on the latest news, promotions, and offers by following us on Twitter at https://twitter.com/uber and liking us on Facebook at https://www.facebook.com/uber. Uber content/messages human- or machine-translated as per device settings; accuracy not guaranteed.

Pigu.lt mobilioji parduotuvė - tai populiariausios elektroninės parduotuvės Lietuvoje Pigu.lt mobilioji aplikacija. Internetinės prekybos programėlė yra prieinama jūsų mobiliajame

įrenginyje per kelias akimirkas.


Atsisiųskite Pigu.lt mobiliąją aplikaciją į savo išmanųjį telefoną ar planšetinį kompiuterį ir naršykite milijonus kasdienių prekių visur, kur turite interneto ryšį.

Internetinės prekybos platforma Pigu.lt yra tam puikus įrankis.


Naudokitės patogia paieška, filtruokite ir suraskite sau tinkamiausias prekes vos keletu piršto paspaudimų. Apsipirkimas internetu niekada anksčiau nebuvo toks lengvas.



Už pirkinius atsiskaitykite saugiai apmokėdami juos jums patogiausiu būdu: banko kortele, elektronine bankininkyste, pavedimu, lizingu ar grynaisiais pinigais atsiėmimo metu. Saugus apsipirkimas internetu yra sėkmingų pirkinių pagrindas.



Internetinio pardavimo platforma leidžia atsiimti prekes Pigu.lt atsiėmimo centruose Vilniuje, Kaune, Klaipėdoje, Šiauliuose ir Panevėžyje, Pigu terminaluose, Lietuvos pašto skyriuose, LP EXPRESS siuntų savitarnos terminaluose ar Omniva paštomatuose. Taip pat siūlome apsipirkti su pristatymu į namus.

_________________________________________________


Pigu.lt yra geriausias įrankis kasdieniams pirkiniams Lietuvoje.



1. Pirkite produktus internete, peržiūrint juos pagal kategorijas.
2. Ieškokite prekių naudodamiesi paieškos, filtravimo bei rūšiavimo funkcijomis.
3. Naršykite ir gaukite panašių prekių rekomendacijas.
4. Gaukite pranešimus ir pirmieji sužinosite apie vykstančias akcijas ir išpardavimus.
5. Pirkite internetu ir mokėkite saugiai per elektroninę bankininkystę, banko pavedimu, lizingu arba grynaisiais.

6. Sekite savo užsakymo būseną ir peržiūrėkite užsakymų istoriją.
7. Peržiūrėkite ir redaguokite savo profilio informaciją.
8. Pasitikrinkite PiguEurų likutį.
9. Peržiūrėkite Pigu VIP KLUBO pasiūlymus.
10. Susikurkite savo norų sąrašą.
11. Pirkiniai programoje Pigu.lt yra dar patogesni! Kompiuteryje, planšetėje ar telefone - savo Pigu.lt pirkinių krepšelį rasite visur. Jums tereikia prisijungti prie savo Pigu.lt paskyros.

__________________________________________________


Pigu.lt mobilioji parduotuvė - tai prekybos centras jūsų kišenėje. Apsipirkti dar niekada nebuvo taip patogu!



Pigu.lt yra internetinė elektronikos parduotuvė su daugeliu produktų kategorijų, įskaitant:
Kvepalai, kosmetika, kompiuterinė technika, buitinė technika ir elektronika, sportas, laisvalaikis, turizmas, santechnika, remontas, šildymas, baldai ir namų interjeras, mobilūs

telefonai, foto ir video, sodo prekės, gyvūnų prekės, kaip reklamoje matytos prekės, vaikams ir kūdikiams, virtuvės, buities, apyvokos prekės, apranga, avalynė, aksesuarai, auto prekės, dovanos, šventinė atributika.



Pirkite internetu geriausius prekės ženklus, įskaitant:

Samsung, Sony, Bosch, Whirpool, Calvin Klein, Chanel, Diesel, Hugo Boss, MSI, Dell, Apple, Asus, Lenovo, Easy Camp, Intex, Hammer, Karcher, Outwell, Adata, Huawei, HTC, Tomtom, Panasonic, Nokia, Hitachi, Stanley, Dunlop, Osram, Royal Canin, Brit, Josera, Friskies, Chicco, Avent, Pampers, Barbie, Fiskars, Keter, Al-ko, iPhone.



Turime daugiau nei 4000 partnerių, tiekiančių prekes Europoje, Azijoje ir Amerikoje. Tai užtikrina pigius aukštos kokybės pirkinius ir platų žinomų gaminių asortimentą.

__________________________________________________


Apsipirkti per programėlę Pigu.lt yra nepaprastai patogu!

Mes visada laukiame jūsų atsiliepimų. Jeigu turite pastebėjimų, nusiskundimų ar pasiūlymų, rašykite mums el. paštu kokybe@pigu.lt.

Linkime Jums gero apsipirkimo Pigu.lt mobiliojoje parduotuvėje!

The idea is simple: you sell your pre-loved stuff to other members who’ll love it again. They get the thrill of unboxing a great find, you get more space at home. It's look-good, do-good, feel-good, for everyone. 

Selling is easy and free
Snap photos of your item, describe it, and set your price. You keep 100% of what you earn.  
• Cash in on your pre-loved clothes, homeware and appliances, electronics, collectables, kids’ toys, and more. 
• Watch your earnings grow. Send your money straight to your bank account. 
• Buyers cover shipping costs. You get prepaid labels that make things simple. 

Shop new-again finds 				
Feel proud of your second-hand discoveries, from designer gems to great-value tech. 
• Fast finds, long-lasting love. There’s a Vinted category for almost everything, use filters to speed up shopping. 
• We’ve got your back. When you buy on Vinted, we cover you with Buyer Protection. For a small fee, you’ll get a refund if your item is lost, damaged in delivery, or significantly not as described. 
• Choose a shipping carrier and have your order sent to your home or a convenient pick-up point.  

Get added confidence
There are 2 verification services on Vinted to give you peace of mind when trading more expensive pieces. 
Item Verification for designer fashion
Have selected items checked for authenticity by our team of experts. 
Electronics Verification 
For certain tech items, get the functionality, condition, and authenticity verified. 
You’ll only receive items that pass the check, or get a refund. Opt to buy verification during checkout. 

There’s a diverse community of second-hand enthusiasts waiting to meet you. Chat with your fellow members, get updates, and manage your orders all in one place. 

Come join us

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/vinted

„EnergySmart" – programėlė „Ignitis" klientams, kuri padės sumaniai naudoti energiją ir taip sumažinti elektros sąskaitą. 

 - Matysite, kokia yra elektros biržos kaina realiu laiku ir kokia ji bus rytoj.
 - Iš anksto pranešime jums apie reikšmingus elektros energijos kainos pokyčius – tiek išskirtinius šuolius, tiek kritimus – tai jums padės efektyviau suplanuoti elektros vartojimą.
 - Matysite savo elektros suvartojimą kas valandą, kas dieną, kas savaitę, kas mėnesį ir galėsite palyginti su praėjusių laikotarpių duomenimis.
 - Sužinosite kiek energijos preliminariai suvartoja namų įrenginiai ir buities prietaisai.
 - Jei turite elektrinę ant stogo arba nutolusiame saulės parke, galėsite stebėti, kiek elektros pagaminote ir kiek jos atidavėte į tinklą – matysite net trijų metų istorinius duomenis.
 - Rasite naudingų energijos taupymo patarimų.
 - Kraunate elektromobilį namuose? Galėsite nustatyti automatinį įkrovimą tada, kai elektra pigiausia.

Jei neturite Nepriklausomo elektros tiekimo sutarties su „Ignitis" ar išmanaus skaitiklio, galėsite naudotis tik dalimi programėlės funkcijų.

Say more with Threads — Instagram’s text-based conversation app.

Threads is where communities come together to discuss everything from the topics you care about today to what’ll be trending tomorrow. Whatever it is you’re interested in, you can follow and connect directly with your favorite creators and others who love the same things — or build a loyal following of your own to share your ideas, opinions and creativity with the world!

A few things you can do on Threads…

■ Access your Instagram followers
Your Instagram username and verification badge are reserved for you. Automatically follow the same accounts you follow on Instagram in a few taps, and discover new accounts too.

■ Share your point of view
Spin up a new thread to express what's on your mind. This is your space to be yourself, and you control who can reply.

■ Connect with friends and your favorite creators
Jump to the replies to get in on the action and react to commentary, humor and insight from the creators you know and love. Find your community and connect with people who care about whatever it is you’re interested in.

■ Control the conversation
Customize your settings and use controls to manage who can see your content, reply to your threads, or mention you. Accounts you’ve blocked will carry over from Instagram, and we’re enforcing the same Community Guidelines to help ensure everyone interacts safely and authentically. 

■ Find ideas and inspiration
From TV recommendations to career advice, get answers to your questions or learn something new from crowd-sourced conversations, thought leaders and industry experts.

■ Never miss a moment
Stay on top of the latest trends and live events. Whether it’s about new music, movie premieres, sports, games, TV shows, fashion, or the latest product releases, find discussions and receive notifications any time your favorite profiles start a new thread.

■ Leap into the fediverse
Threads is part of the fediverse, a global, open, social network of independent servers operated by third parties around the world. Servers share information with each other to enable people to connect and discover new things across the fediverse.
